          <div>PDF + 인쇄본(옵션)로 전달/공유 쉬움</div>
          <div>교육 전문성(퇴임 교사) + 문학박사 해설로 신뢰도 강화</div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="landing-cta landing-variant" data-variant="v2">
      <div class="landing-container landing-cta-inner">
        <div>
          <h2>샘플 리포트로 먼저 확인해보세요</h2>
          <p>
            상담/설명회 없이도 결과 품질을 바로 확인할 수 있어요.
            교사 체험단·학교 시범 운영도 지원합니다.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="landing-cta-actions">
          <a class="landing-button landing-button-primary landing-button-lg" href="#">샘플 무료로 받기</a>
          <a class="landing-link" href="#">교육청/학교 도입 문의</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="landing-footer">
    © 2026 ReadingPRO. All rights reserved.
  </footer>
</div>

<style>
  /* 알림 배너 스타일 */
  .landing-announcements {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
    padding: 12px 0;
    box-shadow: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
  }

  .landing-announcement-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 12px;
    padding: 8px 16px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.15);
    backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
    border-radius: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 8px;
    color: white;
  }

  .landing-announcement-item:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .landing-announcement-icon {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    opacity: 0.9;
  }

  .landing-announcement-text {
    flex: 1;
    font-size: 14px;
    line-height: 1.5;
    font-weight: 500;
  }

  .landing-announcement-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 4px;
    color: white;
    font-size: 13px;
    font-weight: 600;
    text-decoration: none;
    padding: 6px 12px;
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
    border-radius: 6px;
    transition: all 0.2s;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .landing-announcement-link:hover {
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.3);
    transform: translateX(2px);
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .landing-announcement-item {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: flex-start;
      gap: 8px;
    }

    .landing-announcement-link {
      width: 100%;
      justify-content: center;
    }
  }
</style>

<script>
  (function () {
    const page = document.querySelector(".landing-page")
    const buttons = document.querySelectorAll(".landing-toggle-button")
    if (!page || !buttons.length) return

    function setVariant(variant) {
      page.setAttribute("data-variant", variant)
      buttons.forEach((button) => {
        button.classList.toggle("is-active", button.dataset.variant === variant)
      })
    }

    const params = new URLSearchParams(window.location.search)
    const initial = params.get("variant") || "v1"
    setVariant(initial)

    buttons.forEach((button) => {
      button.addEventListener("click", () => {
        setVariant(button.dataset.variant)
      })
    })
  })()
</script>
